          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/B.Test.1532.-step-1.2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>chicken stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[275ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>\n<p>Add the <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>tomato ketchup</strong>, <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>Dijon mustard</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span><strong> sugar</strong></p>\n<p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>bbq sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
